name: Harbhajan Singh
description: Harbhajan Singh Plaha, commonly known as Harbhajan or simply Bhajji or Bhajju Pa, is an Indian cricketer, who has played all formats of cricket for India.  specialist spin bowler, he has the second-highest number of Test wickets by an off spinner

name: Rannvijay Singha
description: Rannvijay Singh Singha is an Indian actor, television personality and VJ. Rannvijay is known for his appearance in MTV Roadies, where he won the show.He has been part of the show from 2004 to 2019 and continues to do so

name: The Great Khali
description: Dalip Singh Rana, better known by the ring name The Great Khali, is an Indian-born American professional wrestler, promoter, model, and actor who is best known for his work in WWE.

name: Ranvir Shorey
description: Ranvir Shorey is an Indian actor and former VJ. Since making his debut in Ek Chhotisi Love Story, he has starred in a number of high-profile films such as Jism and Lakshya

name: Varun Sharma
description: Varun Sharma is an Indian film actor who has starred in commercially successful films including Fukrey, Kis Kisko Pyaar Karoon, Dilwale, Fukrey Returns, and Chhichhore.
